# Trivy CVE exceptions for orkyo-community
#
# Format:
#   CVE-YYYY-NNNNN  # Impact | Reason | Added: YYYY-MM-DD | Review: YYYY-MM-DD
#
# Policy: time-bound only. Review date must be within 14 days of added date.
# Remove entries once the upstream fix is available.

# ── nginx:1.28-alpine — Alpine 3.23 packages not yet rebuilt by nginx upstream ──
# Fix versions exist in Alpine 3.23 but nginx has not published a new 1.28-alpine
# image that includes them. nightly security-refresh.yml will auto-resolve once
# nginx rebuilds. Review: check if nginx:1.28-alpine digest has changed.

