CVE-2026-28387  # HIGH | openssl: use-after-free in DANE TLSA auth | Fix in Alpine 3.23 (3.5.6-r0); nginx:1.28-alpine not yet rebuilt | Added: 2026-05-21 | Review: 2026-06-20
