CVE-2026-21945  # HIGH | openjdk: fix not yet in KC 26.6.2 base image, no package manager | Added: 2026-05-21 | Review: 2026-06-20
CVE-2026-34282  # HIGH | openjdk: Enhance TLS connection handling — fix not yet in KC 26.6.2 base image | Added: 2026-05-21 | Review: 2026-06-20

